---
/**
 * /variants/wordmark — page interne de comparaison wordmark.
 *
 * 4 directions affichées côte à côte sur trois contextes (Nav clair, Hero,
 * Footer dark + balle) :
 *   - Current : Fraunces 900 italic + gradient CSS (état main step-1b)
 *   - A. Wood Sculpted : SVG inline + feTurbulence + feDisplacementMap
 *   - B. Editorial Solid : Fraunces 900 italic couleur unie warm-charcoal
 *   - C. Modern Mono : Big Shoulders Display SCLUBA caps
 *
 * Pas de Base.astro (donc pas de Nav/Footer/i18n) — c'est une page d'audit
 * design ; les fonts sont chargées localement à la page (pas dans Base).
 *
 * Sections rendues explicitement (pas .map()) pour éviter tout souci de
 * résolution de composant Astro depuis un array de références.
 *
 * À retirer du repo quand la direction est figée (PR de cleanup).
 */

import '../../styles/tokens.css';
import WordmarkScluba from '../../components/WordmarkScluba.astro';
import WordmarkWoodSculpted from '../../components/wordmark-variants/WordmarkWoodSculpted.astro';
import WordmarkEditorialSolid from '../../components/wordmark-variants/WordmarkEditorialSolid.astro';
import WordmarkModernMono from '../../components/wordmark-variants/WordmarkModernMono.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>/variants/wordmark — Scluba</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />

  <!-- Fraunces (current, variants A et B) + Big Shoulders Display (variant C) -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link
    rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@1,9..144,900&family=Big+Shoulders+Display:wght@800;900&display=swap"
  />
</head>
<body>
  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Audit design interne</p>
      <h1>Wordmark Scluba — 4 directions</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        Compare les 4 propositions sur les contextes réels du site :
        Nav (fond clair backdrop-blur) + Hero + Footer (fond forest profond).
        Choisis une direction, je nettoie les autres et j'applique sur Nav + Footer.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="variants-grid">

    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!-- CURRENT — baseline step-1b -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <article class="variant" id="v-current">
      <header class="variant-head">
        <h2>Current <span class="tag">baseline · step-1b · live sur main</span></h2>
        <p>Fraunces 900 italic + linear-gradient bois clippé en <code>background-clip: text</code>. Léger, déjà en place. Pas de vraie matière "bois" — juste une coloration.</p>
      </header>

      <section class="ctx">
        <span class="ctx-label">Nav · size 28 · tone wood</span>
        <div class="ctx-frame ctx-frame-light">
          <WordmarkScluba size={28} tone="wood" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="ctx">
        <span class="ctx-label">Hero · size 96 · tone wood</span>
        <div class="ctx-frame ctx-frame-light ctx-frame-tall">
          <WordmarkScluba size={96} tone="wood" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="ctx">
        <span class="ctx-label">Footer · size 48 · tone inverted · withBall</span>
        <div class="ctx-frame ctx-frame-dark ctx-frame-tall">
          <WordmarkScluba size={48} tone="inverted" withBall={true} />
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>

    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!-- A. Wood Sculpted -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <article class="variant" id="v-A">
      <header class="variant-head">
        <h2>A. Wood Sculpted</h2>
        <p>SVG inline avec <code>feTurbulence</code> + <code>feDisplacementMap</code> → vraie texture grain bois sculpté. Garde l'ADN Midjourney en matière réelle. Coût : un peu plus de DOM SVG par instance.</p>
      </header>

      <section class="ctx">
        <span class="ctx-label">Nav · size 28 · tone wood</span>
        <div class="ctx-frame ctx-frame-light">
          <WordmarkWoodSculpted size={28} tone="wood" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="ctx">
        <span class="ctx-label">Hero · size 96 · tone wood</span>
        <div class="ctx-frame ctx-frame-light ctx-frame-tall">
          <WordmarkWoodSculpted size={96} tone="wood" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="ctx">
        <span class="ctx-label">Footer · size 48 · tone inverted · withBall</span>
        <div class="ctx-frame ctx-frame-dark ctx-frame-tall">
          <WordmarkWoodSculpted size={48} tone="inverted" withBall={true} />
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>

    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!-- B. Editorial Solid -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <article class="variant" id="v-B">
      <header class="variant-head">
        <h2>B. Editorial Solid</h2>
        <p>Fraunces 900 italic couleur unie warm-charcoal <code>#2D1B0E</code>, tracking <code>-0.045em</code>. Vibe jeskojets / donmolinico — luxe sobre, contraste AAA.</p>
      </header>

      <section class="ctx">
        <span class="ctx-label">Nav · size 28 · tone wood</span>
        <div class="ctx-frame ctx-frame-light">
          <WordmarkEditorialSolid size={28} tone="wood" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="ctx">
        <span class="ctx-label">Hero · size 96 · tone wood</span>
        <div class="ctx-frame ctx-frame-light ctx-frame-tall">
          <WordmarkEditorialSolid size={96} tone="wood" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="ctx">
        <span class="ctx-label">Footer · size 48 · tone inverted · withBall</span>
        <div class="ctx-frame ctx-frame-dark ctx-frame-tall">
          <WordmarkEditorialSolid size={48} tone="inverted" withBall={true} />
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>

    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!-- C. Modern Mono -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <article class="variant" id="v-C">
      <header class="variant-head">
        <h2>C. Modern Mono</h2>
        <p>Big Shoulders Display 800 caps <code>SCLUBA</code>. Vibe oryzo / umano / drinksom — tech minimal, aucune dépendance Fraunces.</p>
      </header>

      <section class="ctx">
        <span class="ctx-label">Nav · size 28 · tone wood</span>
        <div class="ctx-frame ctx-frame-light">
          <WordmarkModernMono size={28} tone="wood" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="ctx">
        <span class="ctx-label">Hero · size 96 · tone wood</span>
        <div class="ctx-frame ctx-frame-light ctx-frame-tall">
          <WordmarkModernMono size={96} tone="wood" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="ctx">
        <span class="ctx-label">Footer · size 48 · tone inverted · withBall</span>
        <div class="ctx-frame ctx-frame-dark ctx-frame-tall">
          <WordmarkModernMono size={48} tone="inverted" withBall={true} />
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>

  </main>

  <footer class="page-footer">
    <div class="container">
      <p>
        Branche <code>feat/landing-wordmark-variants</code>.
        Quand la direction est choisie : commenter ici, je rebase sur main puis applique le wordmark sur Nav.astro + Footer.astro et je supprime les 3 autres composants + cette page.
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>

<style>
  :global(html), :global(body) {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background: #FAF8F3;
    color: #1A1A1A;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  .page-header {
    padding: 64px 0 48px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
    background: #FBFAF6;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: #6B7280;
  }
  .page-header h1 {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1;
    color: #1A1A1A;
  }
  .lede {
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: #4B5563;
  }

  .variants-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
    padding: 48px 24px;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .variants-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  .variant {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .variant-head {
    padding: 24px 24px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6;
  }
  .variant-head h2 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1A1A1A;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .variant-head h2 .tag {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #9CA3AF;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    background: #F3F4F6;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .variant-head p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #6B7280;
  }
  .variant-head code {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    padding: 1px 5px;
    background: #F3F4F6;
    border-radius: 3px;
    color: #1A1A1A;
  }

  .ctx {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6;
  }
  .ctx:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }

  .ctx-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #9CA3AF;
  }

  .ctx-frame {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    padding: 24px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    min-height: 80px;
  }
  .ctx-frame-tall { min-height: 140px; padding: 32px; }

  .ctx-frame-light {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(14px);
    border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
  }
  .ctx-frame-dark {
    background: #0F2A1E; /* primary-deep — exact footer bg */
    border: 1px solid #1B4332;
  }

  .page-footer {
    padding: 32px 0 64px;
    border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
    background: #FBFAF6;
  }
  .page-footer p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: #6B7280;
    max-width: 70ch;
  }
  .page-footer code {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    background: #F3F4F6;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: #1A1A1A;
  }
</style>
